data.description:
**BACK ON THE MARKET DUE TO BUYER'S LOSS OF FUNDING**

Beautiful farm-style home situated on 9.8 acres! Enjoy sunny days poolside while overlooking the land. The barn features 3 stalls for horses, goats, or other livestock. Bass fish from your very own stocked pond. The chicken coup is a great opportunity to get fresh eggs daily. The home offers an open floorplan ideal for entertaining friends and family. The Primary suite boasts a clawfoot soaking tub and walk-in shower.  This is a must-see!
